*
++MAC($DOC$ZIP) TXLIB(DOCLIB) DISTLIB(ASAMPLIB) SYSLIB(SAMPLIB) .
++MAC($$$$CUST) DELETE .
++MAC($$$$INST) DELETE .
++MAC($$$$M38J) DELETE .
++MAC($$$$RMVE) DELETE .
